<h1 style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 22px; color: #333;">Account Updated</h1>

<p style="font-size: 15px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px;">
  Hi <%= @user.name %>, your Care account was recently updated. If this was you, no action is needed.
</p>

<div style="background-color: #fff8e1; border-left: 4px solid #fbc02d; padding: 14px 18px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 0 0 20px;">
  <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #555; line-height: 1.5;">
    If you didn't make this change, please contact us immediately at
    <a href="mailto:<%= support_email %>" style="color: #fbc02d; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;"><%= support_email %></a>
  </p>
</div>
